{"tid":652443,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"邊個可以話我知，點解我地要供養呢班外國人？","createTime":"2018-05-03T23:55:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-04T12:32:02.000Z","uid":29314,"like":58,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2a8567a5b4bfcfd2031d0baa234d0cd9216b4da8","tid":652443,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T23:55:58.000Z","msg":"呢班每一日都搭火車黎食香港教育福利既人，<br />\n<br />\n佢地父母對香港無作過任何貢獻。<br />\n<br />\n佢地對香港文化一無所知。<br />\n<br />\n佢地唔願意講香港既語言。<br />\n<br />\n佢地唔融入香港既社會。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n究竟，點解我地仲要供養呢班外國人？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/04/075258_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F04%2F075258_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=b94ac12d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"25af32b195b615f17a5c81837f277af3d54edce0","tid":652443,"uid":51701,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T00:12:28.000Z","msg":"因為大家選左泛民同保皇狗<br />\n<br />\n兩邊都靠出賣港人扯貓尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n醫療教育搵工福利全部拎晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再屌你地香港人唔係正統<br />\n就好似班支那賤畜話香港人用顯卡，顯示卡係蝗語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6313748589e1721855e304b7485d07d7712ec3b9","tid":652443,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T00:13:29.000Z","msg":"政府要既只係奴隸"},{"pid":"deccfbab27273714b6fcc6121bdc34bf7ea5fc38","tid":652443,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"25af32b195b615f17a5c81837f277af3d54edce0","tid":652443,"uid":51701,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T00:12:28.000Z","msg":"因為大家選左泛民同保皇狗<br />\n<br />\n兩邊都靠出賣港人扯貓尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n醫療教育搵工福利全部拎晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"